title: Breaking2 Project
content: Breaking2 was a project by Nike to break the 2-hour barrier for the marathon.

title: Kipchoge: The Greatest Marathoner
content: Malcolm Gladwell calls Kipchoge the greatest marathoner who ever lived, and the most beautiful runner who ever lived.

title: Kipchoge Number
content: Gladwell, a runner himself, says that in running circles they have a “Kipchoge number.” This is just like the aforementioned treadmill experiment: how long (in distance) can you keep up with Kipchoge at his marathon pace?

title: Breaking2 Documentary
content: The doc is such a great combination of physiology, psychology, engineering, and the pursuit of excellence—in a movement that is etched into human history.
